sequenceDiagram
    actor 管理员
    participant 浏览器 as 浏览器<br/>statistics.html
    participant SC as AdminStatisticsController
    participant OD as OrderDao
    participant UD as UserDao
    participant VD as VenueDao
    participant DB as MySQL数据库

    管理员->>浏览器: 1. 点击左侧菜单"数据统计"
    浏览器->>SC: 2. GET /statistics_manage
    SC-->>浏览器: 3. 返回HTML空壳页面

    浏览器->>SC: 4. GET /statistics/overview.do
    SC->>OD: 5. countAllOrders()
    OD->>DB: SELECT count(*) FROM `order`
    DB-->>OD: 订单总数
    OD-->>SC: 返回int

    SC->>OD: 6. sumTotalRevenue()
    OD->>DB: SELECT IFNULL(sum(total),0) FROM `order` WHERE state=3
    DB-->>OD: 总营收
    OD-->>SC: 返回int

    SC->>UD: 7. countAllUsers()
    UD->>DB: SELECT count(*) FROM user
    DB-->>OD: 用户总数
    UD-->>SC: 返回int

    SC->>VD: 8. count()
    VD-->>SC: 场馆总数

    SC->>OD: 9. countByState(1)
    OD->>DB: SELECT count(*) FROM `order` WHERE state=1
    DB-->>OD: 待审核数
    OD-->>SC: 返回int

    SC->>OD: 10. countByState(2)
    OD->>DB: SELECT count(*) FROM `order` WHERE state=2
    DB-->>OD: 已通过数
    OD-->>SC: 返回int

    SC->>OD: 11. countByState(3)
    OD->>DB: SELECT count(*) FROM `order` WHERE state=3
    DB-->>OD: 已完成数
    OD-->>SC: 返回int

    SC->>OD: 12. countByState(4)
    OD->>DB: SELECT count(*) FROM `order` WHERE state=4
    DB-->>OD: 已拒绝数
    OD-->>SC: 返回int

    SC-->>浏览器: 13. JSON: 8个数字
    浏览器->>浏览器: 14. 渲染4个数字卡片
    浏览器->>浏览器: 15. 渲染饼图

    浏览器->>SC: 16. GET /statistics/monthlyOrders.do
    SC->>OD: 17. countOrdersByMonth()
    OD->>DB: SELECT DATE_FORMAT(order_time,'%Y-%m'), count(*) GROUP BY month ORDER BY month DESC LIMIT 6
    DB-->>OD: 月度数据数组
    OD-->>SC: 返回List

    loop 遍历每一行
        SC->>SC: Object[]转Map: month, count
    end

    SC-->>浏览器: 18. JSON: [{month,count},...]
    浏览器->>浏览器: 19. 渲染折线图

    浏览器->>SC: 20. GET /statistics/venueRank.do
    SC->>OD: 21. findTopVenues()
    OD->>DB: SELECT venueID, count(*) GROUP BY venueID ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 5
    DB-->>OD: TOP5场馆ID+数量
    OD-->>SC: 返回List

    loop 遍历TOP5场馆
        SC->>VD: 22. getOne(venueID)
        VD->>DB: SELECT * FROM venue WHERE venueID=?
        DB-->>VD: Venue对象
        VD-->>SC: 返回Venue
        SC->>SC: 组装Map: name, count
    end

    SC-->>浏览器: 23. JSON: [{name,count},...]
    浏览器->>浏览器: 24. 渲染柱状图

    浏览器-->>管理员: 25. 页面完整展示
